data.description: Discover this gem located on a corner lot, a single-story haven with 4 bedrooms and 2 baths. Inside, a formal living and dining area await guests. The kitchen boasts upgraded hickory cabinets, pull-out shelves, and newer slate LG appliances. Family room & dining nook. Wood-look tile flows throughout, while the bedrooms offer the comfort of carpet. The spacious master suite is your retreat. A Jack-n-Jill bathroom adds convenience for the secondary bedrooms. Outside, a double-wide gate leads to the backyard with a covered patio, perfect for gatherings. Relax by the tranquil waterfall or enjoy low-maintenance faux lawn. This home blends style and function for the ideal lifestyle.  Just a few blocks to the North Pool Park, convenient to all the amenities of Rancho Sahuarita. EZ access to I-19
